doctype html
html(lang='en')

    head

        meta(charset='utf-8')
        meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no')
        meta(name='description', content='')
        meta(name='author', content='')

        title Clean Blog - Start Bootstrap Theme

        link(rel='icon', type='image/x-icon', href='assets/favicon.ico')

        include includes/css.pug

    body

        include includes/navbar.pug

        // Page Header
        header.masthead(style="background-image: url('assets/img/home-bg.jpg')")
            .container.position-relative.px-4.px-lg-5
                .row.gx-4.gx-lg-5.justify-content-center
                    .col-md-10.col-lg-8.col-xl-7
                        .site-heading
                            h1 Clean Blog
                            span.subheading A Blog Theme by Start Bootstrap

        // Main Content
        .container.px-4.px-lg-5
            .row.px-4.px-lg-5.justify-content-center
                .col-md-5.col-lg-4.mb-3
                    // Post preview
                    a(href='post.html', class='card h-100')
                        img(class='card-img-top', src='assets/img/card-sample-image.png')
                        .card-body
                            h4.card-title
                                | Man must explore, and this is exploration at its greatest
                            p.card-text(style='margin-top: 0;')
                                | Problems look mighty small from 150 miles up

                .col-md-5.col-lg-4.mb-3
                    // Post preview
                    a(href='post.html', class='card h-100')
                        img(class='card-img-top', src='assets/img/card-sample-image.png')
                        .card-body
                            h4.card-title
                                | I believe every human has a finite number of heartbeats. I don't intend to waste any of mine.

            .row.px-4.px-lg-5.justify-content-center
                .col-md-5.col-lg-4.mb-3
                    // Post preview
                    a(href='post.html', class='card h-100')
                        img(class='card-img-top', src='assets/img/card-sample-image.png')
                        .card-body
                            h4.card-title
                                | Science has not yet mastered prophecy
                            p.card-text(style='margin-top: 0;')
                                | We predict too much for the next year and yet far too little for the next ten.

                .col-md-5.col-lg-4.mb-3
                    // Post preview
                    a(href='post.html', class='card h-100')
                        img(class='card-img-top', src='assets/img/card-sample-image.png')
                        .card-body
                            h4.card-title
                                | Failure is not an option
                            p.card-text(style='margin-top: 0;')
                                | Many say exploration is part of our destiny, but it’s actually our duty to future generations.

            // Pager
            .d-flex.justify-content-center.mb-4
                a.btn.btn-primary.text-uppercase(href='#!') Older Posts →

        include includes/footer.pug

        include includes/scripts.pug
